  <brief_title>Safety and Pharmacokinetics of Azelaic Acid Foam, 15% in Papulopustular Rosacea</brief_title>
  <official_title>Investigator-blinded, Randomized, Cross-over, Multiple Dose Phase I Study on Safety and Pharmacokinetics of Topically Applied Azelaic Acid Foam, 15% Compared to Azelaic Acid Gel, 15% in Subjects With Papulopustular Rosacea</official_title>
