  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Assessment of pharmacokinetics of Azelaic Acid Foam after repeated skin application and in
      comparison to Azelaic Acid gel.

      Assessment of safety after repeated skin application.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
